reviewText: I love those films. What I really love about the films is the main star isn't a damsel in distress but the hero.

I really want this series but the description is off. Volume 3 and 5 are in italian only. Volume 1,2 and 4 have the english and italian.  The whole reason I bought this box set was because I thought I was getting the whole series in english. I'm kind of pissed off because I already had 1,2 and 4 and couldn't find 3 and 5. Now I have duplicates and didn't get what was described.
